```

**Channel UI metadata fields:**
- `label`: Display name in UIs
- `selectionLabel`: Text shown when selecting this channel
- `markdownCapable`: Whether the channel supports markdown formatting
- `systemImage`: Icon identifier from system images
- `docsPath` / `docsLabel`: Documentation links

